	   <tr><td colspan=2>I can only agree with you to an extent.&nbsp;&nbsp;Clerics are primarily healers, but we have so many more uses than that.  We have high AC and we can Root, thus making us able to root park a mob away from our group, much like a Paly would, and when things are getting tough, we can Atone that mob so it forgets that we are there.  That is an effective way of helping the group without clicking on the heal button.  We can stun, we can buff, we can pull mobs (in special cases) with our Divine Aura/Barrier, and multiple other things that I won&#8217;t list here.  Being able to utilize our entire arsenal makes us more rounded Clerics as well as IMHO better Clerics.  I could go on and on, but I may have said too much already =)  Clerics are a wonderful class, and one that should not be taken lightly.<br><br>Dinimar Stonecutter<br>CLAW<br>Xegony<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
